S.FORM: Darrell Arthur, unu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput(NBA ), u tabakiay ayaway mimaliay. Darrell Arthur i 2008 a mihcaan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 27, namapili' tu nu New Orleans Hornets putiput. nalecuhan ciniza i 3 a bulad 25 a demiad, 1988 a mihcaan, Darrell Arthur, u miunduay nu kawaw niza. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan u piazihan tu sulit nu ayzaay a tabakiay a mikeliday asaca angangan nu kanatal atu sefu(Lists of National Basketball Association players)
